729168f-b.title: Richmond: Dixon Avenue - Morningstar Road
729168f-b.text:
(1)
397 Morningstar Road, east side, between Dixon Avenue and
Becks Lane. This house belonged to Solon Buffunh (1874-1898) and
C. T. Murphy (1907-1917). The view is north.
May 17, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, another view. The point of vantage is Dixon Avenue.
May 17, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
